TEXT_AETHERYTE_FIRST_OPEN_01<tab>You now have access to the Aethernet.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FIRST_OPEN_02<tab>Quick travel throughout the city can be achieved by simply placing your hand upon Aethernet shards.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_FST<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Gridania. The Blue Badger Gate, the Yellow Serpent Gate, and the airship landing are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_FST_WITH_WHITE_WOLF_GATE<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Gridania. The Blue Badger Gate, the Yellow Serpent Gate, the White Wolf Gate, and the airship landing are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_SEA<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Limsa Lominsa. The Zephyr Gate, the Tempest Gate, and the airship landing are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_WIL<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Ul'dah. The Gate of Nald, the Gate of Thal, the Gate of the Sultana, and the airship landing are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_GOLDSAUCER<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in the Manderville Gold Saucer.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_ROC<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Ishgard. The Gates of Judgement are now accessible as an Aethernet destination.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_IDYLLSHIRE<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Idyllshire. Epilogue Gate is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_IDYLLSHIRE_WITH_QUESTCOMP<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Idyllshire. Prologue Gate and Epilogue Gate are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_KUGANE<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Kugane. The airship landing is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_KUGANE_WITH_QUESTCOMP<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Kugane. The Ruby Price and the Kugane airship landing are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_RHALGRS_REACH<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Rhalgr's Reach. The Fringes Gate is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TOWN_RHALGRS_REACH_WITH_QUESTCOMP<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Rhalgr's Reach. The Fringes Gate and the Peaks Gate are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_DOMAN_ENCLAVE<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in the Doman Enclave. The One River is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_DOMAN_ENCLAVE_WITH_QUESTCOMP<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in the Doman Enclave. The One River and Gangos are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_CRYSTALIUM<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in the Crystarium. Lakeland is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_EURMORE<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Eulmore. Kholusia is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_OLD_SHARLAYAN<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Old Sharlayan.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_OLD_SHARLAYAN_WITH_QUESTCOMP<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Old Sharlayan. Labyrinthos is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_RADZ_AT_HAN<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Radz<var 1F /var>at<var 1F /var>Han.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_RADZ_AT_HAN_WITH_QUESTCOMP<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Radz<var 1F /var>at<var 1F /var>Han. Thavnair is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_0_0<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal. The Arch of the Dawn (Urqopacha) is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_1_0<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal. The Arch of the Dawn (Kozama'uka) is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_2_0<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal. The Arch of the Dawn (Urqopacha) and the Arch of the Dawn (Kozama'uka) are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_3_0<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal. The Arch of the Dawn (Urqopacha), the Arch of the Dawn (Kozama'uka), and Ihuykatumu (Kozama'uka) are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_4_0<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_4_1<tab>The Arch of the Dawn (Urqopacha), the Arch of the Dawn (Kozama'uka), Ihuykatumu (Kozama'uka), and the dirigible landing (Yak T'el) are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_5_0<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Tuliyollal.

TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_TULIYOLLAL_WITH_QUESTCOMP_5_1<tab>The Arch of the Dawn (Urqopacha), the Arch of the Dawn (Kozama'uka), Ihuykatumu (Kozama'uka), the dirigible landing (Yak T'el), and the Xak Tural skygate (Shaaloani) are now accessible as Aethernet destinations.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_SOLUTION_NINE<tab>You have attuned yourself to all the Aethernet shards in Solution Nine.
TEXT_AETHERYTE_FULL_OPEN_SOLUTION_NINE_1<tab>Scanning port nine (Heritage Found) is now accessible as an Aethernet destination.
